import { Link, useParams, useLocation } from "react-router-dom"; import '../index.css' function CourseNavigation() { const links = [ "Home", "Modules", "Piazza", "Zoom Meetings", "Assignments", "Quizzes", "Grades", "People", "Discussions", "Announcements", "Pages", "Files", "Rubrics", "Outcomes", "Collaborations", "Syllabus", "Settings" ]; const { courseId } = useParams(); const { pathname } = useLocation(); return (
  1. courseId
  2. {links.find(link => pathname.includes(link)) || "Home"}
{links.map((link, index) => (
{link}
))}
); } export default CourseNavigation;
